Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libminidjvu0 (= ${binary:Version})
Suggests: minidjvu
Description: Small DjVu encoder/decoder, development files
 MiniDjVu library development files, for DjVu format encoding and
 decoding.
